text: Sergey Tarasevich (born 18 February 1973) is a Belarusian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:People from Svietlahorsk District Category:Belarusian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belarus Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics
